The module creates a filter from a vocabulary of terms for sorting nodes.

    Administration page to activate the vocabulary which will create a block
with a list of terms, if the user JavaScript disabled, but the list will print
button too. When choosing a term from the block, at the end of Url is appended
to the ID of the term.


   Installation:

1. Copy the module folder in sites/all/modules

2. Enable the module on the modules page http://site.com/admin/build/modules

3. On the Settings page http://site.com/admin/build/term_filter
list of all vocabularies include the right and select the
type of display SELECT box or MULTISELECT.

4. On the right page includes a map of the block.

